briefdescription.para: Syncs settings from RAM to .ini file on disk.

detaileddescription.para:
Can be invoked from QML.
Internal function. Do not call if you are not exactly knowing what you want to achieve.

briefdescription.para: Saves settings from RAM to .ini file on disk.
Discards all current settings and loads stored settings from .ini file on disk.
Discards current settings, .ini file and loads default settings.
